    <h3>EHDSBodyStructure → BodyStructureEuCore</h3>
    <p class="lead">
      This page describes the element-by-element mapping from the <a href="https://www.xt-ehr.eu/fhir/models/StructureDefinition/EHDSBodyStructure"><strong>EHDSBodyStructure</strong></a> logical model to the <a href="StructureDefinition-bodyStructure-eu-core.html"><strong>BodyStructureEuCore</strong></a> FHIR profile.
    </p>
